def ConvertDates(dateL):
    yearL = []
    monthL = []
    dayL = []
    for date in dateL:
        monthL.append(int(date[0:2]))
        dayL.append(int(date[3:5]))
        yearL.append(int(date[6:10]))

    df = pd.DataFrame({'year': yearL,
                       'month': monthL,
                       'day': dayL})

    return pd.to_datetime(df)

class Line:
    def __init__(self,y_value,y_label,x_values,x_labels,typeL):
        self.y_value = y_value
        self.y_label = y_label
        self.x_values = x_values
        self.x_labels = x_labels
        self.typeL = typeL

c = calendar.TextCalendar(calendar.SUNDAY)

monthLu = []
for i,r in df.iterrows():
    monthLu.append(int(r.date[0:2]))
    
monthL = range(min(monthLu),max(monthLu)+1);
x_cnt = 0
x_indexL =[]
x_labelL = []
x_monthL = []
x_dayL = []
for m in monthL:
    median_m = median(list(range(1,calendar.monthlen(2019,1)+1)))
    x_labelL.append('')
    x_monthL.append('')
    x_dayL.append('')
    x_indexL.append(x_cnt)
    x_cnt+=1
    for d in c.itermonthdays(2019,m):
        if d != 0:
            if d == median_m:
                x_labelL.append(str(d)+'\n'+calendar.month_name[m]) 
            else:          
                x_labelL.append(str(d))
            
            x_monthL.append(str(m).zfill(2))
            x_dayL.append(str(d).zfill(2))
            x_indexL.append(x_cnt)
            x_cnt+=1

subjectL = list(df['subject'].unique())


# Plot
x_labelL.append('')
x_monthL.append('')
x_dayL.append('')
x_indexL.append(x_cnt)


# build line list
lineL = []
for subjectI, subject in enumerate(subjectL,1):
    subject_df = df[df['subject']==subject]
    l_y_value = subjectI
    l_y_label = subject
    l_x_values = []
    l_x_labels = []
    l_typeL = []
    for i,r in subject_df.iterrows():
        month = r.date[0:2]
        day = r.date[3:5]
        fil = [a and b for a, b in zip([x == month for x in x_monthL], [x == day for x in x_dayL])]
        l_x_values.append(list(compress(x_indexL,fil))[0]);
        l_x_labels.append(list(compress(x_labelL,fil))[0]);
        l_typeL.append(r.SessionType)

    lineL.append(Line(l_y_value,l_y_label,l_x_values,l_x_labels,l_typeL))

import pandas as pd

from bokeh.palettes import Spectral4, all_palettes
from bokeh.plotting import figure, output_file, show
from bokeh.sampledata.stocks import AAPL, IBM, MSFT, GOOG


p = figure(plot_width=800, plot_height=250, x_axis_type="datetime")

for data, name, color in zip([AAPL, IBM, MSFT, GOOG], ["AAPL", "IBM", "MSFT", "GOOG"], Spectral4):
    df = pd.DataFrame(data)
    df['date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['date'])
    p.line(df['date'], df['close'], line_width=2, color=color, legend=name)

p.legend.location = "top_left"
p.legend.title = 'Stock'
p.legend.title_text_font_style = "bold"
p.legend.title_text_font_size = "15pt"

show(p)
